---
title: Shawarma-Spiced Beef Meatball Pitas with Cucumber Salad & Feta Sauce
description: Obsessed with meatball heroes and ready to break out of your usual routine? These sumptuous sandwiches are just the thing. Here, we’ve ditched the marinara sauce and rolls for savory, earthy shawarma-style spices and soft, pillowy pitas. You’ll load in spiced pre-cooked beef meatballs and a lemony cucumber-tomato salad, then drizzle with tangy, creamy feta sauce for a hot, hearty pita sammie in a quick 15 minutes.
